	CERTS Secure Coding recommendation:

	https://www.securecoding.cert.org/confluence/display/cplusplus/DCL32-CPP.+Do+not+declare+or+define+a+reserved+identifierSee also Savannah bug #35745 https://savannah.gnu.org/bugs/?35745

