2008-09-29  flameeyes <flameeyes>

	* configure.ac: Don't use echo -n, use subshells instead.  echo -n is not working on all shells, in particular it does not seem
	to work on Sun /bin/sh shell; instead use subshells to have the same
	output everywhere.

